Paper: hep-th/9401091

Date: 1994-01-19

Title: New N=4 Superfields and Sigma-models

Authors: I.T. Ivanov, U. Lindstrom and M. Rocek

Comments: 11 pages, latex

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B328 (1994) 49-54

In this note, we construct new representations of D=2, N=4 supersymmetrywhich do not involve chiral or twisted chiral multiplets. These multiplets maymake it possible to circumvent no-go theorems about N=4 superspace formulationsof WZWN-models.